      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil half a kettle</p><p>Trim the green stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> off the <strong>aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine </strong>to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and put in the oven for 16-18 min or until the aubergine is golden</p>",
