      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong> and <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the pepper is beginning to soften</p><p>Whilst softening, chop the <strong>olives</strong>,<strong> capers </strong>and <strong>basil </strong>roughly</p><p>Reboil a full kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1615479414401-x200.jpg",
