            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has slightly softened, add the<strong> chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> and <strong>sultana stock</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped olives</strong>, <strong>capers</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>most</strong> of the <strong>chopped basil</strong> (save some for garnish!) and cook for 6-7 min or until the sauce has started to thicken</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
