            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the <strong>roasted aubergine </strong>to the pan with a splash of the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water </strong>and mix everything together – this is your <strong>aubergine caponata</strong></p><p>Tip: Add more of the starchy pasta water if the sauce is looking a little thick!</p>",
      "order": 7,
